{"title":"Wolf Tooth EnCase Pump Gets Smaller 30cc Option","link":"https://theradavist.com/wolf-tooth-encase-pump-30cc/","date":1738075074000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Wolf-Tooth_EnCase-Pump_30cc_3.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Wolf-Tooth_EnCase-Pump_30cc_3.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Wolf-Tooth_EnCase-Pump_30cc_3.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Wolf-Tooth_EnCase-Pump_30cc_3.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/wolf-tooth-components/\" target=\"_blank\">Wolf Tooth</a>‘s <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/2024-radavist-product-awards/\" target=\"_blank\">award-winning EnCase pump line</a> just got a smaller sibling. The Minneapolis-based manufacturer announced the <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=1f8f513b-b98b-4cf0-abf5-e477c8747e9c&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wolftoothcomponents.com%2Fcollections%2Fpumps%2Fproducts%2Fencase-pump-30cc\" target=\"_blank\">EnCase </a><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=1f8f513b-b98b-4cf0-abf5-e477c8747e9c&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wolftoothcomponents.com%2Fcollections%2Fpumps%2Fproducts%2Fencase-pump-30cc\" target=\"_blank\">30cc </a><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=1f8f513b-b98b-4cf0-abf5-e477c8747e9c&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wolftoothcomponents.com%2Fcollections%2Fpumps%2Fproducts%2Fencase-pump-30cc\" target=\"_blank\"> pump today</a> ($64.99) for those riders looking for an even smaller pump – compared to the <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/review-wolf-tooth-encase-hand-pump/\" target=\"_blank\">85cc or 40cc options introduced last year</a> – in their riding kit or bag. This new little EnCase 30cc pump can fit the EnCase Tubeless Tire Plug Tool inside the end opposite of the pump head. Included with the multi-tools is a storage sleeve made of a durable rubber that prevents rattling while making a snug, secure fit in the end of the pump handle.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Wolf-Tooth_EnCase-Pump_30cc_6.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Wolf-Tooth_EnCase-Pump_30cc_6.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Wolf-Tooth_EnCase-Pump_30cc_6.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Wolf-Tooth_EnCase-Pump_30cc_6.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Retail pricing for the EnCase 30cc and 40cc pump sizes start at $64.95 USD, while pricing for the 85cc pump starts at $69.95. Prices increase as multi-tools for internal storage are added. The new Wolf Tooth EnCase Pump is available now on <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=1f8f513b-b98b-4cf0-abf5-e477c8747e9c&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wolftoothcomponents.com%2Fcollections%2Fpumps%2Fproducts%2Fencase-pump-30cc\" target=\"_blank\">WolfToothComponents.com</a> and with any dealer and distributor that stocks Wolf Tooth.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/wolf-tooth-encase-pump-30cc/\">Wolf Tooth EnCase Pump Gets Smaller 30cc Option</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"954b95deb6c15e171955478afc5260c0a6ad71cca82d8a507959ad4d94dd71ae","category":"Cycling"}